* ============================================================
* DotTalk++ Non-Destructive / Non-Complex Command Smoke Test
* ============================================================
* Purpose:
*   Exercise each simple, observer, navigation, help, expression,
*   metadata, and safe table command registered in shell_commands.cpp.
*
* Deliberately excluded:
*   APPEND, APPEND_BLANK, REPLACE, MULTIREP, DELETE, RECALL, UNDELETE,
*   PACK, TURBOPACK, ZAP, CREATE, ERASE, IMPORT, EXPORT, IMPORTSQL,
*   EXPORTSQL, SFTP, WEB, IMAGE, BROWSE/UI commands, SQL INSERT/UPDATE/ERASE,
*   COMMIT/ROLLBACK/TABLE_BUFFER, BUILDLMDB/REINDEX/REBUILD, SCAN/LOOP/IF blocks.
*
* Assumptions:
*   - Run from the DotTalk++ project root or normal runtime directory.
*   - init.ini / dottalkpp.ini provide standard DATA/DBF/INDEXES paths.
*   - BUILDING.DBF, STUDENTS.DBF, TEACHERS.DBF may or may not exist.
*     The script continues even if individual USE/SELECT operations fail.
*   - LIST is developer-only in your current roadmap; use SMARTLIST for order checks.
* ============================================================

ECHO ============================================================
ECHO DOTTalkpp NON-DESTRUCTIVE COMMAND SMOKE TEST
ECHO ============================================================

ECHO
ECHO --- 00. Session / version / environment observers ---
VERSION
ABOUT
STATUS
AREA
AREA51
SHOWINI
DIR
DIR DBF
DIR DBF/X32
DIR DBF/X64
COLOR DEFAULT
BELL
GPS

ECHO
ECHO --- 01. Help / reference / metadata command surface ---
HELP
HELP USE
HELP SELECT
HELP SMARTLIST
HELP FUNCTIONS
* FOXHELP
* DOTHELP
* FOXSTANDARD USE
* FOXSTANDARD LIST
BETA
PSHELL
CMDHELP
COMMANDSHELP
CMDHELPCHK
CMDHELPCHK REF
CMDREL
CMDARGCHK
SECURITY
TABLEMETA

ECHO
ECHO --- 02. Expression engine without DBF dependency ---
CALC 1+1
CALC ABS(-42)
CALC INT(12.99)
CALC ROUND(12.345,2)
CALC MIN(3,1)
CALC MAX(3,1)
CALC BETWEEN(5,1,10)
CALC MOD(10,3)
CALC SQRT(81)
CALC EXP(1)
CALC LOG(10)
CALC LOG10(1000)
CALC SIN(0)
CALC COS(0)
CALC TAN(0)
CALC ASIN(0)
CALC ACOS(1)
CALC ATAN(1)
CALC CEILING(1.2)
CALC FLOOR(1.8)
CALC EMPTY("")
CALC EMPTY(" ")
CALC TRIM("  ABC  ")
CALC DATE()
CALC TODAY()
CALC TIME()
CALC NOW()
CALC CTOD("2000/01/01")
CALC DTOC(CTOD("2000/01/01"))
CALC DTOS(CTOD("2000/01/01"))
CALC YEAR(CTOD("2000/01/01"))
CALC MONTH(CTOD("2000/01/01"))
CALC DAY(CTOD("2000/01/01"))
CALC DOW(CTOD("2000/01/01"))
CALC CDOW(CTOD("2000/01/01"))
CALC CMONTH(CTOD("2000/01/01"))
CALC SECONDS()

ECHO
ECHO --- 03. Education / formula commands ---
BOOLEAN HELP
FORMULA HELP
EVALUATE HELP
NORMALIZE HELP
ASCII
COBOL
CODASYL
RETRO
EXAMPLE
CASE
DRAWIO

ECHO
ECHO --- 04. SQL / SQLite observer surface ---
SQLVER
SQLITE
SQL HELP
SQLSEL HELP
WHERE HELP
SHOW HELP
DBAREAS
DBAREA
WA

ECHO
ECHO --- 05. Schema/workspace/project observers ---
WORKSPACE
WORKSPACE
PROJECTS
WSREPORT
DDL
DDL HELP
FIELDS
STRUCT
FIELDMGR
RULE
RULE STATUS
RULE LIST
RULE PATHS
VALIDATE

ECHO
ECHO --- 06. Try standard schema open safely ---
WORKSPACE OPEN DBF
WORKSPACE
AREA
AREA51
DBAREAS

ECHO
ECHO --- 07. Safe work-area selection attempts ---
SELECT 0
AREA
AREA51
SELECT BUILDING
AREA
SELECT STUDENTS
AREA
SELECT TEACHERS
AREA

ECHO
ECHO --- 08. Safe table observers after schema open ---
FIELDS
STRUCT
COUNT
DISPLAY
LIST 5
SMARTLIST 5
RECNO
GPS
STATUS

ECHO
ECHO --- 09. Cursor movement smoke test ---
TOP
RECNO
DISPLAY
SKIP 1
RECNO
DISPLAY
SKIP -1
RECNO
BOTTOM
RECNO
DISPLAY
TOP
RECNO
GO 1
RECNO
GOTO 1
RECNO
FIRST
RECNO
NEXT
RECNO
PRIOR
RECNO
LAST
RECNO
TOP
RECNO

ECHO
ECHO --- 10. Locate / continue / seek/find smoke test ---
LOCATE
CONTINUE
FIND A
SEEK A
INDEXSEEK A

ECHO
ECHO --- 11. Aggregate observers ---
AGGS
SUM
AVG
AVERAGE
MIN
MAX

ECHO
ECHO --- 12. Filter / relation observer surface ---
SETFILTER
REFRESH
RELATIONS
REL_LIST
REL_REFRESH
REL
TUPLE
TUPTALK
TUPLEDELTA

ECHO
ECHO --- 13. Index/order observer and light navigation surface ---
SETINDEX
SETCNX
SETCDX
SETLMDB
SETORDER
ASCEND
SMARTLIST 5
DESCEND
SMARTLIST 5
TOP
AREA51
LMDB
LMDBDUMP
LMDB_UTIL
CNX
CDX
INDEX

ECHO
ECHO --- 14. Memo / lock / output helpers ---
MEMO
LOCK
UNLOCK
DUMP
* TEXT
PRN

ECHO
ECHO --- 15. Variables and script utilities ---
VAR
DOTSCRIPT
ZIP
ECHO Script echo check

ECHO
ECHO --- 16. Close lifecycle smoke test ---
WORKSPACE CLOSE
WORKSPACE
AREA
STATUS

ECHO ============================================================
ECHO NON-DESTRUCTIVE COMMAND SMOKE TEST COMPLETE
ECHO ============================================================
